</style><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[注意]关于未来。" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/H80Pky34xc4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p> 12月10日，Angel Uto宣布了他的未来发行。发送给发行视频档案的评论是许多英语，而一直在等待天使返回的海外观众和粉丝的回应。</p><p>此外，天使乌拉托（Angel Urato）属于的Vtuber办公室“ Boi Sore”是Persol Innovation经营的虚拟配音演员制作，该作品以插条短语“<em>让我们做，让我们笑，笑。</em> <strong>”</strong>以“ <strong>Koi Itoria</strong> ”的名义加入了。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/voice_ore/status/173333732225650894462?t=b1p04jf5jolrtovqgcrkcqs = 19 </div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="tUqRkJE6Q5"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/mikeneko-joined-vtuber-voice-actress-production-voice-ore-as-koito-ria/">Vtuber Mikineko配音演员Vtuber办公室“ Boi Sore”加入为“ Koi Ito”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Vtuber Mikineko配音演员的Vtuber办公室被录入“ Booso”为“ Koi Ito” -P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/mikeneko-joined-vtuber-voice-actress-production-voice-ore-as-koito-ria/embed/#?secret=gg1xJSenLF#?secret=tUqRkJE6Q5" data-secret="tUqRkJE6Q5" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p>返回的天使的未来活动将被注意到。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@utoch.6000" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">UTOCh。Angel</a> / <a href="https://twitter.com/amatsukauto" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Amatsukauto</a> / <a href="https://twitch.tv/utonyan" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Utonyan</a></p> <cite>YouTube / X（Twitter） / Twitch</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2Y.JP管理代表“ 2号（临时）”</em> /虚拟 / Metavers / vtuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="AG4g1igp7J"><a href="https://en.p2y.jp/amatsuka-uto-returns-to-activity-joined-vtuber-agency-voice-ore/">天冢宇藤回归，加入 VTuber 经纪公司 VOICE-ORE</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“雨藤天冢回归，加入VTuber经纪公司VOICE-ORE” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/amatsuka-uto-returns-to-activity-joined-vtuber-agency-voice-ore/embed/#?secret=PuRE4ouhy2#?secret=AG4g1igp7J" data-secret="AG4g1igp7J" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p>邮政<a href="https://p2y.jp/amatsuka-uto-returns-to-activity-joined-vtuber-agency-voice-ore/">天使并重返活动。加入VTUBER办公室“ Boi Sore”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2Y.JP</a> 。]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://p2y.jp/amatsu-uto-returns-to-joine--vtuber-agency-voice/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 108327</post-id></item><item><title>截至12月10日，VTUBER YouTube频道登记册的平均寄存器数量为2023</title><link/> https://p2y.jp/vtuber- youtube-subscripes-information-anformation-agencies-and-december-10-2023/<comments> https://p2y.jp/vtuber- youtube-subscribers-information-information-agencies-and-and-december-10-2023/＃响应</comments><dc:creator><![CDATA[p2y_adminSat, 09 Dec 2023 15:00:00 +0000 VTuberバーチャルYouTuberチャンネル登録者数(YouTube)バーチャルYouTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=108219 <p> 2023年（Genwa 5）我们将提供有关12月10日YouTube频道注册用户数量的信息。我们将通过主要办公室和组提供有关注册人平均数量的信息。那 […]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-youtube-subscribers-information-agencies-and-groups-december-10