</style><h3 id="outline__1_2" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1_2">参考记录（最大的房屋，组等）</h3><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>办公室 /组名称</strong>-<br>一个组名称，等等。<br><br></td><td><strong>附属ch</strong><br> ——<br> ch数<br>（增加减少）</td><td><strong>平均注册人数</strong>-<br>注册人总数<br>（一周 - 周增加和减少）</td></tr><tr><td><strong>相连接</strong><br>（阶段Connect Ltd。）<br> ——<br>・人才频道 /官方频道<br><br></td><td><strong>22</strong><br> ——<br> 23<br> ├22<br> └1<br> （±0）</td><td> <strong>5279人</strong>（+884人）<br> （在1,128,130中）<br> 1,156030人├1128,130└227,900人（+19,430）△</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> *被认为是加拿大最大的办公室</figcaption></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_3" class="wp-block-heading">人才 /办公室 /团体信息</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="p7SL0MnsiO"><a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-aizawa-ema-reached-500k-youtube-subscribers-the-6th-talent-on-vspo/">Aizawa Emma频道获得了500,000名注册人！ Vtuber的第六人</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Aizawa Emma频道已经实现了500,000个订户！" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-aizawa-ema-reached-500k-youtube-subscribers-the-6th-talent-on-vspo/embed/#?secret=VARx0PDMgU#?secret=p7SL0MnsiO" data-secret="p7SL0MnsiO" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="ynogJ2QcUq"><a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-million-production-announced-800k-total-youtube-subscribers/">VTuber办公室MilliPro宣布频道订阅总数达80万</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ VTUBER办公室米利普罗全频道宣布80万注册人” -P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agenc